{
  "stem": "2684.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once I wrote a letter from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was in Auschwitz a few weeks, they gave us-- I don't know everybody-- to the children block, they distributed a postcard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the postcard was from Walze.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Walze was a holiday spot somewhere in Germany, somewhere around the sea area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the other side you could write five words-- I am very well, kiss, your son, Jules.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my parents received that mail in Hungary during the war, which meant that they knew I am somewhere in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whether they knew that Auschwitz send letter under the name-- because that was the request from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's why they send.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They want to show to the Red Cross that, look, the [NON-ENGLISH] can mail to their parents, or whoever they belong to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the second one, in Dachau, when we freed, after about a month, a Hungarian said that he can't wait for the transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He start his journey back by himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a communist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll never forget, Miklos, he was a very well built, strong guy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't go through the same things like we did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I told him, look, you go back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe things is like here, people hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You go to [NON-ENGLISH] and ask for Fischer Bonde at the goose-- the poultry section.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if you find them, you tell them I'm alive, and you will get either a goose, or a chicken, or whatever they have, they will give it to you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came home, and I said to my mother, you aren't surprised that you see me?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, I already know that you are on the way home because Miklos was at my place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave him a goose.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
